{
  "schema": "cart@1",
  "name": "MS-DOS 4.00",
  "description": "Real MS-DOS 4.00 (Microsoft's MIT-licensed 1988 source), booted from its own boot sector. A writable floppy loaded with EDIT, DEBUG, EDLIN and the classic toolbox.",
  "display": {
    "cover": "msdos4-79.jpg",
    "accent": "#000982",
    "bullets": [
      "The real thing - IO.SYS, MSDOS.SYS, COMMAND.COM",
